HEY ALL! 

SO sorry for being gone for a while, should have given my chars to 
Jer to control while I was gone (but i forgot, so I hope he took the 
initiative and controlled them anyway. 

YES YES YES YES! HAHAHA! 

I'm kinda in an euphoric mood right now, my hockey team just won 
league champions, after eight overtimes of play. Overtimes were 
4-on-4 for 5 mins, then 3-on-3 for 1 min, then 2-on-2 for one min, 
then 1-on-1 for one min then it repeated. In the eight overtime, 
1-on-1, our captain (GREAT guy) made the other team's player and 
goalie look foolish to score with about 10 seconds left on the clock.
GOAL! THE CROWD GOES WILD!

Damn referee... gave me 2 mins for submarining a guy with my 
knee (submarine in hockey = making the other player do a flip, and 
taking out his legs.) and he was trying to hit me! (not the other way 
around)

Heee heee heee... *passes out in his computer chair and 
accidentally sends this message*
